Create virtual environment (make sure to be using python 3.5 or above in your virtualenv)

mkdir Catalog
cd Catalog
virtualenv env
source env/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt



Clone repository

git clone https://github.com/EDUlib/catalog.git



run migrations

cd catalog
python manage.py migrate



How to run

cd catalog
python manage.py runserver 8005


Things to do

a) python manage.py createsuperuser
b) populate table for Ecoles in admin


Modules needed by virtualenv

django==1.11
requests
timestring
python-dateutil
